  "detailed_description": "<strong>Complete</strong><br>Complete is an online co-op survival game where we kill the robots that attack us.<br><br><strong>Characters</strong><br>There are currently 2 different characters in the game and each character has their own unique abilities.<br> <br><strong>Robots</strong><br>Robots are divided into two: close combat and marksman. As you level up, the damage and movement speed of the robots increases.<br><br><strong>Items</strong><br>You can gain features such as shield, movement speed and damage increase by using different items in the game.",
